high_descs: Go left and then turn left before turning right to face the red pillow on the couch.
Pick the paper up from the couch.
Go to the left and face the chair with the computer in it.
Put the paper down on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put a paper on a chair.

high_descs: Turn and go to the couch where the red cushion is.
Pick up the paper that is to the right of the red cushion.
With the paper in hand turn and go to the chair that is to the left of the couch.
Place the paper on the chair cushion on the left side.
Move left to the left side of the large green sofa by the newspaper
Pick up the newspaper on top of green sofa
Carry the newspaper over to the green chair with the laptop on top of it
Place the newspaper on top of the green chair to the left of the laptop
anns.task_desc: Carry a newspaper to the green chair
